          <h3 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">&#xA7; 10</span>.</h3>
          <article class="legalP" id="kapittel-3-paragraf-1-ledd-1">Denne forskriften trer i kraft 1. januar 1993.</article>
        </article>
      </section>
